definitions.definition: A city , the county seat of Kankakee County , Illinois , United States .
An unincorporated community in LaPorte County , Indiana , United States .
A river , the Kankakee River in Indiana and Illinois , which is a tributary of the Illinois River .
Three townships in the United States, in Illinois (1) and Indiana (2), listed under Kankakee Township .
